      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STREET SIXTY SIX (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.62) at this track behind Bragging Rights in a Special conditions H. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Key chance in this line up. JILL'S FANTASY (3) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 3.5 lengths away in second (23.17) at Mt Gambier in a Grade 5 over 400m. Expected to be in the finish again. PAW PASCAL (6) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 2 lengths away in third (22.31) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Will give a great sight again. BUSH BUDDY (2) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
